<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>@ViewData["Title"] - Diet</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/Contacts.css" asp-append-version="true" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/Diet.styles.css" asp-append-version="true" />
</head>
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Контакти";
}
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-7">
                <h1 class="text-left">Контакти</h1>
                <p class="text-left">Личната комуникация с теб е много важна за екипа ни. Не се колебай да се свържеш с нас на посочените по-долу координати. 
                Отговаряме в рамките на един работен ден.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-5">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <h3 class="text-left">Контакти</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                    <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-pencil"></span></div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="row">
                   <label class="label col-md-2 control-label">Имейл</label>
                    <div class="col-md-10">
                       <input type="Email" class="form-control" name="Email" placeholder="Имейл">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                   <label class="label col-md-2 control-label">Парола</label>
                    <div class="col-md-10">
                       <input type="Password" class="form-control" name="Password" placeholder="Парола">
                       <input type="checkbox"> <small>Запомни ме</small>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                   <label class="label col-md-2 control-label">Съобщение</label>
                    <div class="col-md-10">
                       <textarea class="form-control"></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <label class="label col-md-2 control-label">Пол</label>
                    <div class="col-md-10">
                       <input type="radio" value="male" nme="gn"> <small>Мъж</small>
                       <input type="radio" value="female" nme="gn"> <small>Жена</small>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <label class="label col-md-2 control-label">Държава</label>
                    <div class="col-md-10">
                       <select class="form-control">
                           <option>Турция</option>
                           <option>България</option>
                           <option>Гърция</option>
                           <option>Полша</option>
                           <option>Русия</option>
                           <option>Нидерландия</option>
                       </select>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <a href="#"><div class="btn btn-info">Изпращане</div></a>
                <a href="#"><div class="btn btn-warning">Отказ</div></a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>